#. <section class="sutta" id="sn54.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn54.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Dutiyabhikkhusutta"
msgstr "16. Several Mendicants (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinne kho te "
"bhikkhū bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then several mendicants went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one "
"side. The Buddha said to them:"

msgctxt "sn54.16:1.2"
msgid ""
"“atthi nu kho, bhikkhave, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro dhamme "
"paripūreti, cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti, "
"satta dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā dve dhamme paripūrentī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, is there one thing that, when developed and cultivated, "
"fulfills four things; and those four things, when developed and cultivated, "
"fulfill seven things; and those seven things, when developed and cultivated, "
"fulfill two things?”"

msgctxt "sn54.16:1.3"
msgid ""
"“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā … pe … bhagavato sutvā bhikkhū "
"dhāressantī”ti."
msgstr "“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. …”"

msgctxt "sn54.16:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Atthi, bhikkhave, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro dhamme paripūreti, "
"cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti, satta dhammā "
"bhāvitā bahulīkatā dve dhamme paripūrenti."
msgstr "“There is, mendicants."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:2.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro dhamme "
"paripūreti, cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti, "
"satta dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā dve dhamme paripūrenti?"
msgstr "And what is that one thing?"

msgctxt "sn54.16:2.2"
msgid ""
"Ānāpānassatisamādhi, bhikkhave, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta "
"bojjhaṅge paripūrenti, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiṃ "
"paripūrentīti."
msgstr ""
"Immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is one thing that, when developed "
"and cultivated, fulfills the four kinds of mindfulness meditation. And the "
"four kinds of mindfulness meditation, when developed and cultivated, fulfill "
"the seven awakening factors. And the seven awakening factors, when developed "
"and cultivated, fulfill knowledge and freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.336"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:3.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvito ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti?"
msgstr ""
"And how is mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated so as to "
"fulfill the four kinds of mindfulness meditation?"

msgctxt "sn54.16:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā "
"nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ "
"upaṭṭhapetvā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or "
"to an empty hut. They sit down cross-legged, with their body straight, and "
"establish mindfulness right there. …"

msgctxt "sn54.16:3.3"
msgid "So satova assasati, satova passasati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:3.4"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dīghaṃ vā assasanto ‘dīghaṃ assasāmī’ti "
"pajānāti, dīghaṃ vā passasanto ‘dīghaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti, rassaṃ vā "
"assasanto ‘rassaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:4.2"
msgid "sabbakāyappaṭisaṃvedī … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:4.3"
msgid ""
"‘passambhayaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ "
"kāyasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:4.4"
msgid ""
"kāye kāyānupassī, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī sampajāno "
"satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:4.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:4.6"
msgid "Kāyaññatarāhaṃ, bhikkhave, etaṃ vadāmi, yadidaṃ—assāsapassāsaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:4.7"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, kāye kāyānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.337"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:5.1"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pītippaṭisaṃvedī … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:5.2"
msgid "sukhappaṭisaṃvedī …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:5.3"
msgid "cittasaṅkhārappaṭisaṃvedī …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:5.4"
msgid ""
"‘passambhayaṃ cittasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ "
"cittasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:5.5"
msgid ""
"vedanāsu vedanānupassī, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:5.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:5.7"
msgid ""
"Vedanāññatarāhaṃ, bhikkhave, etaṃ vadāmi, yadidaṃ—assāsapassāsānaṃ sādhukaṃ "
"manasikāraṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:5.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, vedanāsu vedanānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati "
"ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:6.1"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cittappaṭisaṃvedī … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:6.2"
msgid "abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:6.3"
msgid ""
"‘samādahaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘samādahaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:6.4"
msgid ""
"‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:6.5"
msgid ""
"citte cittānupassī, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:6.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:6.7"
msgid ""
"Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, muṭṭhassatissa asampajānassa ānāpānassatisamādhibhāvanaṃ "
"vadāmi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:6.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, citte cittānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati "
"ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:7.1"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aniccānupassī … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:7.2"
msgid "virāgānupassī … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:7.3"
msgid "nirodhānupassī … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:7.4"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:7.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:7.6"
msgid ""
"So yaṃ taṃ hoti abhijjhādomanassānaṃ pahānaṃ taṃ paññāya disvā sādhukaṃ "
"ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:7.7"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, dhammesu dhammānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati "
"ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:8.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvito kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi evaṃ bahulīkato cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.338"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:9.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā kathaṃ bahulīkatā satta "
"bojjhaṅge paripūrenti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:9.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati—upaṭṭhitāssa "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno sati hoti asammuṭṭhā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:9.3"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno upaṭṭhitā sati asammuṭṭhā—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:9.4"
msgid ""
"satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, satisambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:10.1"
msgid ""
"So tathāsato viharanto taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinati pavicarati "
"parivīmaṃsamāpajjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:10.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tathāsato viharanto taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya "
"pavicinati pavicarati parivīmaṃsamāpajjati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:10.3"
msgid ""
"dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, "
"dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. "
"(2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:11.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinato pavicarato parivīmaṃsamāpajjato "
"āraddhaṃ hoti vīriyaṃ asallīnaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:11.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinato "
"pavicarato parivīmaṃsamāpajjato āraddhaṃ hoti vīriyaṃ asallīnaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:11.3"
msgid ""
"vīriyasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, vīriyasambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, vīriyasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:12.1"
msgid "Āraddhavīriyassa uppajjati pīti nirāmisā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:12.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno āraddhavīriyassa uppajjati pīti nirāmisā—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:12.3"
msgid ""
"pītisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, pītisambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, pītisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.339"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:13.1"
msgid "Pītimanassa kāyopi passambhati, cittampi passambhati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:13.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pītimanassa kāyopi passambhati, cittampi "
"passambhati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:13.3"
msgid ""
"passaddhisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"passaddhisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, passaddhisambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:14.1"
msgid "Passaddhakāyassa sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:14.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno passaddhakāyassa sukhino cittaṃ "
"samādhiyati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:14.3"
msgid ""
"samādhisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"samādhisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, samādhisambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:15.1"
msgid "So tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:15.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ "
"ajjhupekkhitā hoti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:15.3"
msgid ""
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:16.1"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:16.2"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:16.3"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati—upaṭṭhitāssa tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno sati "
"hoti asammuṭṭhā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:16.4"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno upaṭṭhitā sati hoti asammuṭṭhā—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:16.5"
msgid ""
"satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, satisambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti—satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati … pe …."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:17.1"
msgid "So tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:17.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ "
"ajjhupekkhitā hoti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:17.3"
msgid ""
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:17.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā evaṃ bahulīkatā satta "
"bojjhaṅge paripūrenti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.340"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.16:18.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā kathaṃ bahulīkatā "
"vijjāvimuttiṃ paripūrenti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:18.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ "
"virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ; dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe "
"… upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.16:18.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā evaṃ bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiṃ "
"paripūrentī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how the seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated so as to "
"fulfill knowledge and freedom.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.16:18.4"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
